OUR MISSION
• Upholds human dignity and provides
impartial aid to the vulnerable
• Offers volunteer opportunities for members
to assist those in need selflessly
TRAINING
~ First Aid
.

respond effectively to emergencies

.

YU15
SERVICE
• Gains insight into humanity's diverse needs
and challenges through community service
• Fosters empathy and understanding
• Develops a deeper appreciation for the
world's complexities and the importance of
compassion
• Broadens perspectives on global issues and
social responsibility
FRIENDSHIP FUNCTIONS
• Provides platforms for students to expand
their horizons and forge new friendships
• Fosters social interaction, cultural exchange,
and the creation of lasting bonds
• Enriches students' experiences and create a
sense of camaraderie within the Red Cross
community
